MuleDefinitionParser, MuleDefinitionParserConfiguration, org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.BeanDefinitionParser
public class ForwardingRouterDefinitionParser
extends AbstractSerialDelegatingDefinitionParser

In addition to a ForwardingConsumer router, implicitly create a NullComponent service as a placeholder. We use AbstractSerialDelegatingDefinitionParser to be able to create 2 beans from a single element. We use a ParentDefinitionParser for the NullComponent, because it needs to be set not on (the surrounding element), but on (one level up).
